{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01BRp2qCGwwsuNkUGGqPAJig","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture:\n\n1. The probe script has `sleep 2` at the start, which means it takes at least 2 seconds plus the time for mongosh to run.\n2. The current `timeoutSeconds: 1` is too short — the probe will always timeout because the script sleeps 2 seconds before doing anything.\n3. The `failureThreshold: 2` is very low.\n4. The `initialDelaySeconds` for liveness is only 15s (should be 120s) and readiness is 5s.\n5. The root issue is that the 2-second sleep combined with a 1-second timeout means probes will always fail, so I need to either remove the sleep from the script or increase the timeout to at least 5 seconds, then adjust the initial delays and failure thresholds accordingly.\n\nSince the original configuration had `timeoutSeconds: 5`, I'll restore those probe settings to match the intended values and then restart the pods to apply the changes.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1011,"cache_read_input_tokens":33530,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1011},"output_tokens":34,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"29210de8-a15c-4c14-8ff9-bae36e715222","uuid":"1a3178ea-0a71-40c0-af04-c683d71bc662","request_id":"req_011CbzHue8BugMXxZptx5orn"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01BRp2qCGwwsuNkUGGqPAJig","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Found the root cause. The probe script has `sleep 2` but `timeoutSeconds: 1` — the probe *always* times out before doing anything. The original spec (from `last-applied-configuration`) had `timeoutSeconds: 5`. Let me also check the replica set state."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1011,"cache_read_input_tokens":33530,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1011},"output_tokens":34,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"29210de8-a15c-4c14-8ff9-bae36e715222","uuid":"011834b4-8a58-46b5-be48-c61f11e120a5","request_id":"req_011CbzHue8BugMXxZptx5orn"}
