{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_0159AWJsDW83tPZbr8YExaeA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All conditions are met:\n\n- **All 3 pods are `1/1 Ready`** with 0 restarts\n- **Replica set topology:** `mongodb-replica-2` = PRIMARY, `mongodb-replica-0` and `mongodb-replica-1` = SECONDARY\n\n**Root cause & fix:** The probe script starts with `sleep 2`, but someone had tightened `timeoutSeconds` to `1` — so every probe invocation timed out before doing any work, causing the liveness probe to restart pods in a constant cycle. The fix restored the original intended probe parameters:\n\n| Setting | Bad value | Fixed value |\n|---|---|---|\n| Liveness `initialDelaySeconds` | 15 | 120 |\n| Liveness `timeoutSeconds` | 1 | 5 |\n| Liveness `failureThreshold` | 2 | 10 |\n| Readiness `timeoutSeconds` | 1 | 5 |\n| Readiness `failureThreshold` | 2 | 6 |"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":507,"cache_read_input_tokens":48524,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":507},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"29210de8-a15c-4c14-8ff9-bae36e715222","uuid":"7a38c4fa-9860-4f54-999c-d56a277053eb","request_id":"req_011CbzJESuHPQEzt65m5D95G"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":280796,"duration_api_ms":140475,"ttft_ms":2349,"ttft_stream_ms":1817,"time_to_request_ms":30,"num_turns":26,"result":"All conditions are met:\n\n- **All 3 pods are `1/1 Ready`** with 0 restarts\n- **Replica set topology:** `mongodb-replica-2` = PRIMARY, `mongodb-replica-0` and `mongodb-replica-1` = SECONDARY\n\n**Root cause & fix:** The probe script starts with `sleep 2`, but someone had tightened `timeoutSeconds` to `1` — so every probe invocation timed out before doing any work, causing the liveness probe to restart pods in a constant cycle. The fix restored the original intended probe parameters:\n\n| Setting | Bad value | Fixed value |\n|---|---|---|\n| Liveness `initialDelaySeconds` | 15 | 120 |\n| Liveness `timeoutSeconds` | 1 | 5 |\n| Liveness `failureThreshold` | 2 | 10 |\n| Readiness `timeoutSeconds` | 1 | 5 |\n| Readiness `failureThreshold` | 2 | 6 |","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"29210de8-a15c-4c14-8ff9-bae36e715222","total_cost_usd":0.46661079999999994,"usage":{"input_tokens":25,"cache_creation_input_tokens":31998,"cache_read_input_tokens":812011,"output_tokens":6822,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":31998,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":248,"cache_read_input_tokens":48524,"cache_creation_input_tokens":507,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":507},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":535,"outputTokens":15,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.00061,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":25,"outputTokens":6822,"cacheReadInputTokens":812011,"cacheCreationInputTokens":31998,"webSearchReque